OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778702756
OL,3,CInquests into deaths of six babies
OL,4,Cmurdered by Lucy Letby pushed back to
OL,5,C2027
OL,7,FInquests into the deaths of six babies
OL,8,Fwho Lucy Letby was convicted of
OL,9,Fmurdering have been delayed until 2027.
OL,11,FThe infants died at the Countess of
OL,12,FChester Hospital in 2015 and 2016 when
OL,13,FLetby was employed as a nurse in the
OL,14,Fneonatal unit.
OL,16,FFull hearings into their deaths were
OL,17,Fscheduled for September 2026 after
OL,18,Feach inquest was previously opened and
OL,19,Fsuspended.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
