PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778702756
OL,3,CInquests into deaths of six babies
OL,4,Cmurdered by Lucy Letby pushed back to
OL,5,C2027
OL,7,FHowever, the hearings have been re-
OL,8,Flisted to provisionally begin on 10
OL,9,FMay 2027 after it was announced that
OL,10,FLady Justice Thirlwall's inquiry
OL,11,Freport into how the nurse was able to
OL,12,Fcommit her crimes will not be
OL,13,Fpublished until at least September.
OL,15,FA statement on the Thirlwall Inquiry
OL,16,Fwebsite said: "The inquiry can now
OL,17,Fgive a further update regarding
OL,18,Fpublication of the final report.
OL,26,@xD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778702756
OL,3,CInquests into deaths of six babies
OL,4,Cmurdered by Lucy Letby pushed back to
OL,5,C2027
OL,7,F"The report will be published at the
OL,8,Fearliest practical date. However that
OL,9,Fwill not be until after the summer
OL,10,Frecess of Parliament.
OL,12,F"We will give further updates
OL,13,Fregarding publication in due course."
OL,15,FOn Wednesday, the suspensions of the
OL,16,Finquests of Baby C, Baby D, Baby E,
OL,17,FBaby I, Baby O and Baby P were
OL,18,Fformally continued at Cheshire
OL,19,FCoroner's Court.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUuD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
