PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778702756
OL,3,CInquests into deaths of six babies
OL,4,Cmurdered by Lucy Letby pushed back to
OL,5,C2027
OL,7,FA statement issued on behalf of the
OL,8,Fcourt said: "The coroner considers it
OL,9,Fappropriate to maintain the suspension
OL,10,Fin order to ensure that the findings
OL,11,Fand recommendations of the Thirlwall
OL,12,FInquiry can be fully considered before
OL,13,Fthe inquests proceed."
OL,15,FThe matter will be further reviewed in
OL,16,FNovember, added the statement.
OL,26,@pD@MOUuD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
