CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778702756
OL,3,CInquests into deaths of six babies
OL,4,Cmurdered by Lucy Letby pushed back to
OL,5,C2027
OL,7,FLetby, 36, from Hereford, is serving
OL,8,F15 whole-life orders after she was
OL,9,Fconvicted at Manchester Crown Court of
OL,10,Fmurdering seven infants and attempting
OL,11,Fto murder seven others between June
OL,12,F2015 and June 2016.
OL,14,FShe was twice denied permission to
OL,15,Fappeal against her convictions in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
