FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778702756
OL,3,CInquests into deaths of six babies
OL,4,Cmurdered by Lucy Letby pushed back to
OL,5,C2027
OL,7,FThe Criminal Cases Review Commission,
OL,8,Fwhich investigates potential
OL,9,Fmiscarriages of justice, is
OL,10,Fconsidering evidence presented on her
OL,11,Fbehalf by an international panel of
OL,12,Fmedics who claim poor medical care and
OL,13,Fnatural causes were the reasons for
OL,14,Fthe babies collapsing.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
