PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1778702756
OL,3,CInquests into deaths of six babies
OL,4,Cmurdered by Lucy Letby pushed back to
OL,5,C2027
OL,7,FAn inquest into the death of Baby A `
OL,8,Fanother of Letby's victims ` was held
OL,9,Fin October 2016 and a narrative
OL,10,Fconclusion said it could not be
OL,11,Fdetermined what caused the youngster's
OL,12,Fcollapse and subsequent death or
OL,13,Fwhether it was due to a natural or
OL,14,Funnatural event.
OL,16,FLetby was removed from clinical duties
OL,17,Fin July 2016 after consultant
OL,18,Fpaediatricians raised concerns that
OL,19,Fshe may be deliberately harming
OL,20,Fbabies, but those fears were not
OL,21,Fmentioned at Baby A's inquest.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
